snippet.title: Sky Oceans: Wings For Hire - Official Gameplay Trailer | Guerrilla Collective 2024
snippet.description:
Here's a fresh look at Sky Oceans: Wings For Hire in this new trailer for the upcoming game that is an homage to JRPG classics. The trailer showcases gameplay and some of the features you can expect, including ship customization and more. Sky Oceans: Wings For Hire will be available on PC (Steam, Epic Games Store, GOG), PS5, Xbox Series X/S, and Nintendo Switch. 

Set in the open skies, experience adrenaline-filled turn-based dogfights in Sky Oceans: Wings For Hire, as you take the role of captain and unite a party of rag-tag sky pirates setting upon an unforgettable, touching journey.
